ot fully surrendered.\n \n*        *  =\r\n      *\n \n&gt; How to measure it?\n \nOne can measure it by seeing how one is in=\r\nternally reacting to challenging circumstances that would earlier provoke l=\r\nust, anger, greed, jealosy etc inside one.\n \nHowever, what will one do by m=\r\neasuring? It is not like one can turn a knob based on the measurement to co=\r\nrrect it.\n \nIn fact, when surrender is completeone you will stop measuring =\r\nor even thinking about how to measure it.\n \nBest regards,\nNarasimha\n-------=\r\n------------------------------------------------------------\n  Free Jyotish=\r\n Software, Free Jyotish Lessons, Jyotish Writings,\n&quot;Do It Yourself&quot; ritual =\r\nmanuals for short Homam and Pitri Tarpana:\n                  http://www.Ved=\r\nicAstrologer.org\n     Films that make a difference: http://SaraswatiFilms.o=\r\nrg\n     Spirituality: http://groups.yahoo.com/group/vedic-wisdom\n  Jyotish =\r\nwritings: http://groups.yahoo.com/group/JyotishWritings\n-------------------=\r\n------------------------------------------------\n \n---- vedic_pathak &lt;vedic=\r\n_pathak@...&gt; wrote: \n&gt; Namaste,\n&gt; \n&gt; &gt; Easiest thing to do is Ishwar(=\r\nIshwari) pranidhana. Surrender to &gt;God. I freely admitted to the Lord when =\r\nI had His darshana that I &gt;was a complete fool \n&gt; \n&gt; I sincerely wish to su=\r\nrrender to Mother completely. I am trying hard. I wish to surrender my ego,=\r\n anger, passions as well as all good qualities....\n&gt; \n&gt; How to achieve it e=\r\nffectivey? How to measure it?\n&gt; \n&gt; Regards,\n&gt; \n&gt; Utpal\n&gt; \n&gt; --- In vedic-wi=\r\nsdom@yahoogroups.com, Narasimha PVR Rao &lt;pvr@...&gt; wrote:\n&gt; &gt;\n&gt; &gt; Forwarding=\r\n a note from Manish...\n&gt; &gt;  \n&gt; &gt; &gt; &gt; &gt;I agree with Dinesh. Only very advanc=\r\ned sadhakas will be able to identify\n&gt; &gt; &gt; rnas / karmic debts and know how=\r\n/where/why they are to be paid off. The rest\n&gt